      "id": 7,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Why some RAG panels can be empty\nThe Prometheus charts on this page only show activity observed since the current API process started. After a restart, they stay blank until a fresh `/api/chat` request completes. The Postgres chart still shows historical API-chat sessions from earlier runs.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
